ooking at (and listening\nto) while answering a question about an image - do not help people better\npredict its behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2017 17:58:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Oct 2017 17:55:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-03"}
