e los velocities of the thin and thick disc in\nthe b/p bulge ($\\Delta v_{los}$) correlates with the initial difference between\nthe radial velocity dispersions of the two discs ($\\Delta \\sigma$) . We\ntherefore conclude that stars in the bar - b/p bulge will have considerably\ndifferent morphologies and kinematics depending on the kinematic properties of\nthe disc population they originate from.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2017 18:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 May 2017 15:15:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
